CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, National Edition, October 15, 1938, pg. 21, reads: "Actress Visits Pittsburgh - Mrs. Frances Williams, an actress in stage production, 'You Can't Take It With You,' shown at the Nixon theatre in Pittsburgh last week. Sitting with Mrs. Williams is Detective John Brown of New York.  They were guests at the Loendi Club."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of actor Frances Williams wearing fox fur stole standing by mantle in Loendi Club
